        @Deprecated
public Type getGenericType()
        已过时。 
        从类复制的说明: Annotated
        JDK declared generic type of the annotated element; definition of what exactly this means depends on sub-class. Note that such type cannot be reliably resolved without TypeResolutionContext, and as a result use of this method was deprecated in Jackson 2.7: see Annotated.getType() for replacement.

        getGenericType 在类中 Annotated

      • call

        public final Object call()
                  throws Exception
        从类复制的说明: AnnotatedWithParams
        Method that can be used to (try to) call this object without arguments. This may succeed or fail, depending on expected number of arguments: caller needs to take care to pass correct number. Exceptions are thrown directly from actual low-level call.

        Note: only works for constructors and static methods.

        指定者:
        call 在类中 AnnotatedWithParams
